organization_short_description:
Tesla Properties is a Dubai based Real Estate Brokerage firm concentrating on Residential and Commercial properties throughout Dubai, UAE. As one of Dubai's leading Real Estate Brokers, we provide a full range of services for all your real estate needs and strive to give our clients the highest quality service and value for their investments and property management solutions. We provide high-quality service that includes: in-house convincing and documentation processing, mortgage assistance, professional real estate consultancy, property management. With highly motivated, dedicated and goal-oriented Consultants and back office support staff, the company strengthens its competitiveness to provide you with the best and suitable options to suit your specific investment needs. With substantial knowledge of dynamic marketing experience and expertise in both the local and Gulf region, it is our mission to provide our clients with the latest information in relation to up to date market trends in Dubai. So whether you're looking to buy, sell, or rent a Dubai property, Tesla Properties Real Estate is ready to serve you.
Tesla properties one of the leading real-estate company that deals with the top most developers in UAE .Today, it is possible to collect information just with the push of a button. You can easily find your dream place to live that can be called homes. We will do all the legwork for you. Just show up at your begin a new comfortable life. All our apartments are beautifully designed and the neighborhoods are very appealing. And we do it as per terms and conditions of our clients with our team that consists of real estate experts, hospitality professionals, globetrotters, etc.

name: Sara Hamam
title: Marketing Director
headline: Marketing Director at Les Mills IMEA
organization_name: Les Mills India, Middle East & Africa (LMIMEA)
organization_short_description:
Les Mills has been delivering life-changing fitness experiences for over 50 years. Now an international fitness brand, we mix music, motivation and movement for millions around the globe through our world-class fitness programs. Our mission is simple – to create a fitter planet. 

We blur the boundaries of physical and digital experiences to bring our club partners ultimate fitness solutions. Feel our love for live group fitness with the iconic barbell workout BODYPUMP. Pedal through utopia and dystopia all in the same workout with the immersive cycle experience of THE TRIP. Reserve your spot in the front row of martial arts inspired BODYCOMBAT or any of our 1000+ workouts available on LES MILLS+.

Creating a fitter planet means more than exercise. We're dedicated to carbon neutrality, measuring and offsetting carbon dioxide emissions for each of our global offices. Through our BORN TO MOVE program and partnership with UNICEF, we're united in our ambition to create a world where every child survives and thrives. 

We're in the business of strength and allowing teammates to play to theirs. Diversity, equity and inclusion are a mindset and a culture; a healthy work-life balance an essential, and encouragement to ‘exercise your passion' fundamental.


لقد قامت شركة ليزملز بتقديم تجارب لياقة بدنية مغيرة للحياة لأكثر من 50 عاماً. الآن هذه العلامة التجارية العالمية للياقة البدنية، تقوم بمزج الموسيقى والتحفيز والحركة للملايين حول العالم من خلال برامج اللياقة البدنية ذات المستوى العالمي. مهمتها بسيطة - إنشاء كوكب ـأكثر لياقة.  

بدأت قصة ليزملز في عام 1968 عندما بدأ ليزملز، وهو رياضي أولمبي، أول صالة ألعاب رياضية له في أوكلاند، نيوزيلندا، لقد كانت عملية بسيطة ، وتمارين أساسية للقوة وتمارين الكارديو لمجتمع صغير من الرياضيين. الآن، بعد مرور 50 عامًا، أصبح مركزاً للثورة العالمية - وجهة نابضة بالحياة حيث يخلق أفضل مواهب اللياقة البدنية في العالم طرقًا جديدة للحصول على لياقتهم، والجمع بين الموسيقى والحركة ثم نقلها إلى العالم. 

كان ابن ليز فيليب ملز هو من قاد التغيير. ع

name: Debbie Gobbett
title: Marketing Director
headline: Marketing Director
organization_short_description:
WHO WE ARE: Press Play Online was formed in 2014 when we saw how important video was for websites and social media marketing - back then social media was in it's infancy, so we were delighted to be at the start of an exciting boom that was to be video for web! Derek has been filming wildlife, adrenalin activities and weddings since 1996 and I started as his assistant photographer at weddings back in 1997, so we used what we knew in photography & video and applied it to the new platform of the world wide web.

WHAT WE DO: video Production! Since 2014 we have filmed and photographed a fabulous variety of businesses, big and small, telling their unique stories and creating reach for their brands. From high end Real Estate to wine farms and golf courses, commercial coaching videos to health & fitness companies, small charities to investment videos for kids clothing brands and everything in-between. 

WHY WE DO IT: We love getting the shot that no one else can! Aerial Photography and Film is getting that birds eye view of a property or golf course that goes beyond the naked eye. Also, we're pretty nosey and love seeing the interior decor of other people's homes (for our real estate photography and video) we do love a social  game of golf (for our golf course marketing videos) and we are natural story tellers and love a beautiful shot for our wedding photography & videos.

CONTACT US: If you would like some creative video or photo imagery for your website or social media, do give me a call on +44 7557 397723 I would love to chat about your visual ideas and work with you

Cryo Services is on a mission to provide you with a one stop shop for all your installation and servicing needs of cryogenic equipment.

organization_short_description:
Founded in 2010 in the UK / Founded in 2023 in the UAE.

Ambitek specialise in providing permanent & contract solutions.

We have a successful track record of placing candidates with skills and experience within Assembly & Maintenance, Design & Drawing Office, Foundry & Metallurgy, Machining & Tooling, Quality & Inspection, Welding & Fabrication, Site Based Engineering, Skilled Trades, Professional & White-Collar Engineering, Production & Logistics and Controls & Instrumentation.

We recruit on behalf of a wide range of clients including established SME's to FTSE 100 & Fortune 500 organisations.
